## ğŸŒ Endpoints

### ğŸ”‘ Authentication
| Method | URI                    | Action           | Permissions | Body |
|--------|------------------------|------------------|-------------|------|
| POST   | /api/auth/register     | Register user    | Public      |      |
| POST   | /api/auth/login        | Login user       | Public      |      |

### ğŸ‘¥ Users
| Method | URI                               | Action              | Permissions | Body |
|--------|-----------------------------------|---------------------|-------------|------|
| GET    | /api/users/profile                | View user profile   | User        |      |
| PUT    | /api/users/profile/update         | Update user profile | User        |      |
| GET    | /api/users                        | View users          | Superadmin  |      |
| PUT    | /api/users/:id/role               | Update user role    | Superadmin  |      |
| PUT    | /api/users/:id/follow             | Follow user         | User        |      |
| PUT    | /api/users/deactivate             | Deactivate user     | User        |      |
| PUT    | /api/users/superactivate/:id      | Reactivate user     | Superadmin  |      |
| DELETE | /api/users/:id                    | Delete user         | Superadmin  |      |

### ğŸ“ Posts
| Method | URI                              | Action                | Permissions | Body |
|--------|----------------------------------|-----------------------|-------------|------|
| POST   | /api/posts                       | Create post           | User        |      |
| DELETE | /api/posts/:id                   | Delete post           | User        |      |
| PUT    | /api/posts/:id                   | Update post           | User        |      |
| GET    | /api/posts/own                   | Get own posts         | User        |      |
| GET    | /api/posts                       | Get all posts         | Public      |      |
| PUT    | /api/posts/like/:id              | Like post             | User        |      |
| GET    | /api/posts/timeline              | Get timeline posts    | User        |      |
| PUT    | /api/posts/comment/:id           | Add comment to post   | User        |      |
